{
  "texts": [
    "The Global Risk Index can be extended with automation.",
    "We highlight our automation approach in the appendix.",
    "Building on our pilot results, a future automated misuse-relevant capability assessment system could provide:",
    "Recurrent risk monitoring: Periodic or continuous evaluation of newly published scientific literature, tool releases and technological developments to identify emerging risks as they appear with evaluation against our pre-established rubrics.",
    "Dynamic risk scoring: Adaptation of misuse-relevant capability assessments based on evolving capabilities, diffusion of knowledge and implementation of safeguards."
  ]
}